none: Collection
Prison Rodeo Programs
Coverage
Huntsville, Texas
Date
Description

The Prison Rodeo Program, Official Souvenir booklet, includes 60 pages of photographs depicting the 54th Annual Prison Rodeo held in Huntsville, Texas, including photographs of the Texas Prison Board, features and articles for events and performances, and photographs of the facilities within the prison.
